        <item>
            <title>0.3.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:02:56 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:channel>beta</sparkle:channel>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### What's new
- **Theme Studio** — create and manage your own terminal color themes. Open it from Settings → Appearance → Customize Colors… to edit the 16 ANSI colors plus background, foreground and cursor, with a live preview.
- **Light & dark per theme** — a theme can hold separate light and dark palettes and switch automatically with your macOS appearance.
- Custom themes appear in Settings → Appearance alongside System, Dark and Light, so you can fix low-contrast colors (like washed-out yellow on light backgrounds).
]]></description>
